OL,3,CNHS Trust fined #500,000 over death of
OL,4,C'beautiful, vibrant' Alice Figueiredo
OL,6,FThe mother of 22-year-old, who took
OL,7,Fher own life on a hospital ward, has
OL,8,Fcriticised staff for "indifference,
OL,9,Fignorance, even at times cruelty," as
OL,10,Fthe NHS Trust which treated her was
OL,11,Ffined more than #500,000 for her death.
OL,13,FAlice Figueiredo, who was described as
OL,14,Fa "beautiful, vibrant young woman",
OL,15,Ftook her own life in a mental health
OL,16,Funit at Goodmayes Hospital, Redbridge,
OL,17,Fafter more than 10 similar attempts.
