OL,3,CNHS Trust fined #500,000 over death of
OL,4,C'beautiful, vibrant' Alice Figueiredo
OL,6,FThe former head girl's death, on July
OL,7,F7 2015, came after plastic items that
OL,8,Fshe had used to self harm were not
OL,9,Fremoved from the communal toilets on
OL,10,FHepworth Ward .
OL,12,FFollowing an Old Bailey trial, North
OL,13,FEast London NHS Foundation Trust
OL,14,F(NELFT) was found guilty of failing to
OL,15,Fensure the safety of a non-employee.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, the Trust was fined
OL,18,F#565,000 over the health and safety
OL,19,Fbreach ` plus #200,000 costs.
