OL,3,CNHS Trust fined #500,000 over death of
OL,4,C'beautiful, vibrant' Alice Figueiredo
OL,6,FWard manager Benjamin Aninakwa, 54, of
OL,7,FGrays in Essex, was convicted of
OL,8,Ffailing to take reasonable care for
OL,9,Fthe health and safety of patients on
OL,10,Fthe ward Ms Figueiredo was on.
OL,12,FJudge Richard Marks KC sentenced him
OL,13,Fto six months in prison, suspended for
OL,14,F12 months, plus 300 hours of unpaid
OL,15,Fwork.
OL,17,FHe said: "Her death at such a young
OL,18,Fage in the circumstances in which it
OL,19,Foccurred is a terrible tragedy."
