OL,3,CNHS Trust fined #500,000 over death of
OL,4,C'beautiful, vibrant' Alice Figueiredo
OL,6,FThe judge said the accessibility of
OL,7,Fplastic in the communal toilets was a
OL,8,F"very serious problem" and them not
OL,9,Fbeing removed was a "complete failure".
OL,11,FHe told Mr Aninakwa: "You knew that
OL,12,Fshe was suicidal ` she was the only
OL,13,Fpatient on the ward that was. Your
OL,14,Fnegligent breach of duty went on for
OL,15,Fweeks."
OL,17,FEarlier, Alice's mother and former
OL,18,Fhospital chaplain Jane Figueiredo said
OL,19,Fthey had been treated with "dismissive
OL,20,Fcontempt, belittling and playing down"
OL,21,Ftheir "well-founded" concerns in 2015.
