OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement,
OL,7,Faddressing the ward manager, she told
OL,8,Fthe court: "What she did not like on
OL,9,Fyour watch in 2015, Mr Aninakwa, was
OL,10,Fbeing treated by some staff with
OL,11,Funkindness, harshness, indifference,
OL,12,Fignorance, even at times cruelty or
OL,13,Fbeing endangered and left at risk by
OL,14,Fneglectful and incompetent staff some
OL,15,Fof whom seemed to be clueless about
OL,16,Ftheir duties and responsibilities a
OL,17,Ffact you were often in denial of."
