OL,3,CNHS Trust fined #500,000 over death of
OL,4,C'beautiful, vibrant' Alice Figueiredo
OL,6,FShe described her daughter as a
OL,7,F"uniquely beautiful, brave,
OL,8,Faffectionate generous, kind,
OL,9,Fcolourful, creative and luminous
OL,10,Fspirit".
OL,12,FAlice was first admitted to the
OL,13,FHepworth Ward in May 2012 with a
OL,14,Fdiagnosis including non-specific
OL,15,Feating disorder and bipolar affective
OL,16,Fdisorder.
OL,18,FShe had attempted suicide 18 times and
OL,19,Fthey were recorded in ward notes and
OL,20,Fother hospital records.
