OL,3,CNHS Trust fined #500,000 over death of
OL,4,C'beautiful, vibrant' Alice Figueiredo
OL,6,FAninakwa, who was subject to a
OL,7,Fperformance improvement plan, had
OL,8,Ffailed to remove plastic that could be
OL,9,Fused for self-harm and failed to
OL,10,Fensure incidents of self-harm were
OL,11,Frecorded, considered and addressed,
OL,12,Fjurors had heard.
OL,14,FHe and the trust had denied
OL,15,Fwrongdoing, but declined to give
OL,16,Fevidence.
OL,18,FThe investigation into Ms Figueiredo's
OL,19,Fdeath began in 2016, but charges were
OL,20,Fnot brought until September 2023.
