OL,3,CNHS Trust fined #500,000 over death of
OL,4,C'beautiful, vibrant' Alice Figueiredo
OL,6,FThe trust was cleared of corporate
OL,7,Fmanslaughter, and Aninakwa was found
OL,8,Fnot guilty of manslaughter by gross
OL,9,Fnegligence.
OL,11,FThe first corporate manslaughter trial
OL,12,Fagainst an NHS trust collapsed in 2016
OL,13,Fafter a judge ruled there was no case
OL,14,Fto answer.
